if mibBuilder.loadTexts: bdifthTemplateName.setStatus('current')
if mibBuilder.loadTexts: bdifthTemplateName.setDescription("This object specifies a unique name associated with the threshold template by the management client, and provides a non-volatile 'handle' for the template. The name must not include whitespace characters. After this value has been written to the startup configuration, the agent must retain the value until a management client deletes it. The level of retention must span reboots and re-initializations of the agent, including those that result in different assignments to the value of bdifthTemplateIndex associated with this template. Once an entry has been activated, this value cannot be modified. In order to use a new value of bdifthTemplateName, a new template must be defined.")
